<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages/player.css">
</head>
<body>

  <%- include("../partials/header") %>

  <main>
    <section class="player-auth-section">
      <div class="container player-auth-container">
        <div class="player-auth-card">
          <span class="section-tag">Recuperacao de senha</span>
          <h1>Esqueci minha senha</h1>
          <p>
            Durante a Beta, a recuperacao de senha e feita pelo suporte. Abra um ticket no Discord
            informando seu e-mail e nick.
          </p>

          <div class="player-auth-error">
            <strong>Proxima fase</strong>
            <p>
              Recuperacao automatica por e-mail com token que expira em 30 minutos,
              SMTP e tabela PasswordResetToken fica reservada para producao.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="player-auth-footer">
            <a href="<%= discordInvite %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Abrir Discord</a>
            <a href="/entrar">Voltar ao login</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>
